data.description: OWNER IS MOTIVATED!!  NEW FLOORING COMING SOON! The owner is updating the flooring with all new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the entire home. You're not going to want to miss this single-story mid century modern block home in a highly sought central location in Seminole! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage home is located on a quiet street within a fantastic neighborhood just minutes from the beautiful Gulf Beaches. You'll love the bright and open floor plan with a large chef-inspired kitchen; ideal for hosting and entertaining. The kitchen features a GE stainless steel double oven and a GE monogram electric cooktop, all surrounded by beautiful hard wood cabinetry for plenty of storage and counter space. The home has a split floor plan layout with the primary bedroom and bathroom on one side and the secondary bedrooms and bathroom on the opposite side. The backyard patio creates some additional living space perfect for a playroom or home office space. The backyard is fully fenced and offers lots of privacy!  The home is right down the street from the Pinellas Trail, providing easy access to multiple parks and green space close by. The Seminole City Center is close by, offering lots of shopping and dining options. You'll have peace of mind knowing this home is located in a non-evacuation zone and not in a flood zone.  It's also just under 23 miles away from TPA International Airport, 25 miles from Downtown Tampa, and 16 miles from Downtown St Pete so you'll have easy access to all the events and hotspots Tampa Bay has to offer. All of this while living ten minutes from the Gulf Beaches! Be sure to schedule a showing today!
